4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive 16-week bootcamp to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer, tailored for beginners with no prior experience. Instructors include experts with extensive backgrounds in AI and Machine Learning, such as Sayyed Nezhadi and Francesco Pugliese. The curriculum covers Python, SQL, and various libraries to build predictive models using supervised and unsupervised learning techniques. Participants will engage in real-life scenarios and complete projects from development to deployment while focusing on privacy and security. Classes are limited to 12 students and available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop